<A HREF="eqnews.php3"><B>Second Expansion Pack Announced:</B></A><BR>
<FONT SIZE="2" FACE="ARIEL">
Check our <A HREF="eqnews.php3">EQ News</A> section for more on the announcement of a 2nd expansion pack for EverQuest.</FONT><BR><BR>

<A HREF="main.phtml#1.0 Poll"><B>Polls:</B></A><BR>
<FONT SIZE="2" FACE="ARIEL">
Here are the results from the last poll. The question was <I>"Which of the following common complaints about Kunark would you most like to see addressed?"</I></FONT><BR><BR>

<FONT SIZE="1" FACE="ARIEL">
1. More spell drops   17.03% (62 votes)<BR>
2. More loot   23.63% (86 votes)<BR>
3. More experience   21.43% (78 votes)<BR>
4. Better framerates   23.35% (85 votes)<BR>
5. Less bugs   14.56% (53 votes)<BR>
<B>-------------------</B><BR>
<B>Total Votes:</B> 364</FONT><BR><BR>

<FONT SIZE="2" FACE="ARIEL">
All the complaints pretty much share equal preference among the voters, with #4 Better Framerates and #2 More Loot being almost dead even. Hopefully, with Velious, Verant will not make the same mistakes and we won't need a 1 GHZ machine to play the new zones *grin*.<BR><BR>

In light of the big announcement about the upcoming expansion pack, this weeks new poll will ask <I>"Do you intend to purchase the expansion pack "The Scars of Velious" when it is released?"</I>.</FONT><BR><BR>

<A HREF="maps.php3"><B>Maps:</B></A><BR>
<FONT SIZE="2" FACE="ARIEL">
Yes, we do have maps of Velious! While these are old Beta maps, I am sure there will be many similarities with the new continent when it gets released. Also, Muse over at <A HREF="http://www.eqatlas.com" TARGET="_new">EQ Atlas</A> has just released his new maps of Lower Guk...</FONT><BR><BR>

<FONT SIZE="2" FACE="ARIEL">1. <A HREF="map_search.php3?action=zone&add_zone=Velious">Velious</A> - Early Beta Maps</FONT><BR>
<FONT SIZE="2" FACE="ARIEL">2. <A HREF="map_search.php3?action=zone&add_zone=Guk%20-%20Lower">Lower Guk</A> - By EQ Atlas</FONT><BR><BR>

<A HREF="screenshots.phtml"><B>Daily Kunark Image:</B></A><BR>
<FONT SIZE="2" FACE="ARIEL">
We still need more screenshots for our "Kunark Daily Image" on our main page, so if you see a nice sunset, dungeon, beast or castle.... make sure you take a nice picture and <A HREF="mailto:madwand@home.com">mail</A> it to us !
</FONT><BR><BR>

<B><I>MadWand</I></B></FONT></TD></TR></TABLE>	
